-Teltoli-

With a grunt, she picks up a largish peice of metal and throws it up to Plintissa, and then dusting herself off.

"Seems like fairly strong stuff.." She murmers, mostly to herself. She looked back and saw the strange blue thing still behind her. Teltoli wondered what it was.. almost to the point where it was getting annoying. She heard low murmers coming from the bush, and two pairs of eyes on her.

She throws her hands up in exasperation, and turns to use her zoom-up vision at this bot. Her scanners identified that it was Alliance. And had an almost dragon like form. 

She didn't trust those Alliance guys.. they were too shifty.. but she hoped the bot would come out soon and state his business if he wanted anything to do with her..
